Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:09.01,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I had lost my way during my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:17.02,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Only my soul was wandering, while I stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:25.28,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}But right now, I'm walking to a distant place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:33.53,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}That's right, ever since I met you on this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:41.96,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}The travellers witnessed the song, the forbidden song,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:52.72,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And I became attached to it as I heard it alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:01:00.81,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}If the world I saw in my dreams exists somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:09.20,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Let's go search for it, beyond the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.37,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Whether it's a freezing dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.58,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A dry midday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:21.75,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A shivering night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:28.00,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}or the ends of the Earth, let's go and see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:38.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the port city, Pattsio!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:55.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the city has a lot of good food.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:56.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:01:59.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't need to hide your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:01.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:03.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been in that village for several hundred years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:07.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,so there must be tales left behind of how you look in your human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:12.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,"Horo sometimes appears in the village as a beautiful maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:15.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks as if she is in her adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:18.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She has long, flowing hair, like a wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:23.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She also has a white tipped tail, and her hair is a light, beautiful brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:25.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for keeping her appearance a secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:27.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,she promises an abundant wheat harvest the following year."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:29.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got all your characteristics down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:33.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All who have seen me have doubted me as much as you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:37.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't believe it if I don't show them my ears and tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:42.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:44.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They've forgotten about me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,As for me, I hope that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:55.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:03:01.40,Chapter Name Title Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf and Business Ability
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:09.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This city is just as I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:11.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:13.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Those apples look tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:14.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:20.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They look {\i1}really{\i0} tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:24.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:29.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, an acquaintance of mine predicted the future demand for apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:31.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He risked half of his assets on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:33.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure where he got the apples,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:36.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's several times wealthier now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:38.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have hopped on it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:42.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:44.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, there's a lot of risk to it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:47.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,As for me, I would invest in ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:48.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:51.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life will be in danger if there are shipwrecks,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:53.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but if it goes well, there'll be huge profits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:57.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Merchants would contract with us and pay a fee to rent ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:03.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, they'll be renting ships, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:06.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of the fee to rent the ship, we can also charge them a duty for their cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:09.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Apples...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:13.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat apples...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:15.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Go buy some with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:24.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would normally buy this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:28.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who told me to buy {\i1}some{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:31.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know the meaning of restraint?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You had better earn your keep for your meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Purposefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:41.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretended not to notice, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:44.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels empowering to know what someone wants, and that they're in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:46.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my money, wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:50.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Horo the Wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can earn this much money whenever I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:55.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:59.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to pay the lodging and meal charges with that money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you ate them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:04.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Apples are the fruit of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:07.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He tempted me with their sweet smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:10.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so wise, why can't you overcome it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many who lose their appetite,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:16.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but there is no reason to abstain from eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:20.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be conducting our transactions here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance certainly is big, but
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:27.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,looking at the building, I think there are bigger ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:30.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it's the third largest one in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:36.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's merely a branch of a big company that's located in a country far south.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:39.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we'll take advantage of their status as foreigners,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:40.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and sell it to them at a high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:42.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And, above all-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:46.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be multifarious information coming in from the branch and head offices, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:49.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,By doing business outside of your own town,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:52.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you are better able to adapt to the changes in currency.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:58.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I aim to ask that Zeiren boy about his story nonchalantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We might discover what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:04.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Milone Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought wheat here about three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'd like to sell some fur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:13.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, that's perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:17.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for doing business with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Craft Lawrence, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:21.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored that you remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:25.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:28.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you wanted to discuss selling your furs today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:29.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are seventy in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:36.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,These are fine marten furs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:40.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There haven't been many peasants coming in with marten furs this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:43.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be busy with their farm work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:46.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, here I am with an abundance of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:49.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so there are seventy in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:52.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, as with previous transactions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,does this suit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:57.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred and thirty-two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In what currency?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thoreni silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:09.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to look at the gloss of these furs that appear once every several... no, ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:12.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't dulled at all, even when soaked by the rain en-route.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:15.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, the gloss is excellent, as is the lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:19.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a trimmed fur you don't see often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:23.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping we would have a good relationship from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:27.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a far-off company, but I completely agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:32.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in regards to our developing relationship, how does one hundred and forty sound to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:46.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the market price. So, how is his offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:47.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:53.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you fine with the offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:56.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred and forty Thoreni silver coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you said, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:05.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, y-yes, I did indeed say one hundred and forty Thoreni silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:10.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be a respectable merchant, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:14.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, is that why you pretended not to notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's so, I can't just let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:21.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Forgive me, is there something I overlooked?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:24.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, you shouldn't be playing tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't mean to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell him, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:39.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take one and try smelling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:48.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:51.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... the smell of fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:53.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:56.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The forests and fields are abundant with fruit this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:09:01.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Those pelts are from animals that seem to have passed through those forests just days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:06.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They ate the fresh fruit, so a sweet smell exudes from their fur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly does smell sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:11.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how fine these marten furs are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:15.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It took two big men to strip off the fur!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:16.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was tough, since it was strongly attached to the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:21.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to hold back, try and pull on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull on it more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strong and stretchy like a beast,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:31.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,warm as the spring sunlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:33.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,repels water when rained upon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll be treated to this fragrance when you smell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:38.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Among clothes made from fur, these would make you turn and smell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:44.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just imagine these clothes on the market; their smell could come from only one source!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:47.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that they will become an expensive style that you can sell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:52.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this is your last chance to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:57.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How about two hundred Thoreni silver coins, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:04.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How about three silver coins per fur?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:06.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That is to say, two hundred and ten silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:09.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there other companies, master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:14.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take them for two hundred and ten silver coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:18.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:25.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:33.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This grape wine is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:37.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Aren't you going to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:39.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:42.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever done any trading?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:46.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did my actions hurt your pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:51.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure when, but it was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:56.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the idea of a smart merchant who passed by the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:59.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something I thought of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:11.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even realize it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:11.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:16.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't smell anything when I slept on them last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:19.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's because of the apples I bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's their fault for not catching on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:28.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, they must be impressed to know that there is such a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:30.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:34.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing comes of getting angry after you've been fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:39.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only first rate if you can be impressed to find that such a trick exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:43.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, did you look into what you mentioned before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:44.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:49.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I haven't found anything concerning a new silver coin being issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:58.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there might be a trick to Zeiren's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:01.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I profit and not retain any losses, it should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:05.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, cheers to our reunion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:15.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking wine this good must mean that your fur trading went well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:16.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:20.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's great! That means I'll be profiting more, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:23.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:24.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:28.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for telling me which currency is being revalued,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:31.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you want a part of the profit as the fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:33.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you said, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:36.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that currency revaluation story true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:40.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, first of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:44.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,it's just some information I heard when I was living in a mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:47.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it can be trusted, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:49.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:52.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There weren't any sordid dealings going on, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:58.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was intending to refuse if you said you were sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:00.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no suspicious story like that, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:02.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what will be your share?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:06.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes, just as we discussed, ten Thoreni silver coins,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:10.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and ten percent of your profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bit conservative, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:16.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if you were to lose out, I wouldn't be able to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:19.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for curbing my profits,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:24.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I will only return the ten silver coins we agreed to if you were to take on a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:26.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, that should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:31.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'd like it if we could meet the notary tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, to our profit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,To our profit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:45.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Falam silver coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's a fake Mariin silver coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the noble Lord Dadionche's silver coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:56.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'll remember them better after you use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:57.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue after a good night's rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:01.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:04.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start here, so listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:04.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:06.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thoreni silver coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Philling silver coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Liuto silver coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:11.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Fake Mariin silver coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Falam silver coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:15.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,King Rambalt Tokt silver coin. {/dunno}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:17.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsfing Cathedral silver coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:19.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Fake Mitsfing Cathedral silver coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:21.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,St. Mitsfing silver coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, I'm sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:27.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A smart choice from Horo the Wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:31.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there so many, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a limit to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:36.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When a country is born or collapses, more are issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:41.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, more are issued because of the influence of powerful locals and the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:43.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are also counterfeit coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:47.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Liuto silver coins were once called fake Thoreni silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:49.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:07.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I got some good information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:08.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:12.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, boss, I'll be taking my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:13.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:16.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a killing, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And you stay as beautiful as you are, madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:25.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a noisy guy until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:29.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the silver coin in question, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:30.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:33.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a credible and strong currency in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:35.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Credible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are several hundred different currencies,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:40.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and the silver and gold content is constantly changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:45.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,To begin with, the face value of the currency is higher than the silver or gold it's made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use it if it's not credible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:54.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how is it? Did you find out anything after knowing which silver coin it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:56.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:59.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than finding out something, I thought of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:14.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you realize?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:16.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:21.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A Philling silver coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:24.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This has a high content of pure silver,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:26.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and is quite popular on the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:28.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Thoreni silver coin's rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:32.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A country flaunting its power through its currency is the same in every era.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:33.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:35.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When a foreign currency is introduced to the market,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,that country will take the lead in economic activity,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's no different to us than losing a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:43.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in order to defeat your rivals, you have to raise the silver's purity?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:48.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so it's quite possible that Zeiren isn't lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:51.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My ears aren't perfect, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You thought I'd get angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:56.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:17:00.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have gotten angry if you had confronted me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:04.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A person I know is in the money-exchanging business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Money-exchanging?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:12.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,To be truthful, you can't tell the purity of the currency.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, raising and lowering the purity is common,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:16.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and these money-exchangers are sensitive to the change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:20.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a slight change can become a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:24.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why when there's going to be a big change, there's an omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to remember it all right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:31.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take about a month, but I'll explain it all to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:33.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's that, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:37.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's time to change the purity of the currency,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:40.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,they first raise the purity just slightly and then judge the people's reactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:43.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the response, they might see to raising the purity more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:48.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:50.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:51.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:53.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:55.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name, little lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:58.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:17:59.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:02.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What a splendid name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:05.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do her yet, Lawrence?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:08.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll seduce her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine with you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's troubling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:21.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, my business comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:25.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any Thoreni silver coins that were recently issued?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:28.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:31.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We handle them every day and even we can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:33.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to melt it down and find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be foolish, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:38.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you let me have a look, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:40.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.73,0:18:46.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:55.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of impossible, Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:19:00.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There seem to be money-exchangers who can do that after many years, but
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,it's really just a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, it can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:14.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:17.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He was quite interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:19.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He likes women he can't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:24.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did the purity of the silver go up or down?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:27.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten better even though you were so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ears moved a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:31.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:35.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, I was surprised you didn't say it there and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:37.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was something like gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:38.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:41.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a bit jealous weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:42.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gratitude for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:46.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:49.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Males are all stupid and jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:52.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And females are stupid to be happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots are everywhere you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:56.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, what about the purity of the silver?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:20:01.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was slight, but the new one sounded a bit more dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:02.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Dull?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:06.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means the silver content went down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:08.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Zeiren was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:12.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fighting against time to try to make a profit with a currency that's weakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:16.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a difference if I change it back once the value lowers a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:19.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, the local currency will return to normal, and there {\i1}will {\i0}be a profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something I can do in half a year, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:26.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there even a way for Zeiren to earn a profit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you weren't tricked?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:32.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Tricked?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:34.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:37.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean he tricked me for the ten silver coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:39.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At worst, your profit will be zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:43.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if the currency goes down and you have a loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:45.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you just need to have that kid return the coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:49.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Conversely, if the currency goes up, you hand him a share of the profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:52.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there was a chance to make a profit,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no possible way for that kid to be at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:57.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:00.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,People are smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:02.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:04.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:09.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it normal to see the silver's purity go down?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:14.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they normally take great care and slowly raise the silver's purity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:18.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And then a deal concerning the purity of silver coins blows in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:21.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:25.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When we hunt, we sometimes climb the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:30.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're on a tree, surprisingly enough, it's easy to find the prey's hiding places.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:33.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At times like those, you need to find a new perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:35.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A new perspective?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:40.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it wasn't that kid who was scheming something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:46.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like the kid needs to get his profit directly from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:53.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He could've been asked by someone else to bring that unusual deal to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.34,0:21:55.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:59.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a trick where you buy weakening currencies to gain a profit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:02.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you thought of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:03.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:06.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to, this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:08.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Milone Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:19.91,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven apples on the witch's tree
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.91,0:22:25.29,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,With seven seeds to plant inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:30.47,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,In spring time I grew a magic song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.47,0:22:33.21,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Then skipping along,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:35.77,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I sang the song to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:41.20,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I look at the world through apple eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.20,0:22:46.53,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And cut myself a slice of sunshine pie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:51.87,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I danced with the peanuts for the flies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:54.50,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Till someone had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:57.56,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,To say hello for every good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:23:02.52,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw some sugar stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:07.61,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put them in a jar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:10.18,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:13.62,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:17.48,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little wolf inside a cart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.48,0:23:18.83,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,You say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:23.12,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And off I go from June to May
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:29.01,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:32.66,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.63,0:23:44.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Helpless Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:49.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Helpless Partner.
